midnight the Los Angeles fire marshalls stormed in and took action.
That annual party has come to embody the magazine's happy symbiosis
with Hollywood. By Alex Kuczynski. With graphics.
</P>
<P>
   BOOKSELLERS-MEDIA (New York) _ Facing intense competition, the
nation's trade association for independent booksellers is creating
