<HEADLINE>
PONDERING A WHITE HOUSE SHRINK 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.)  (The Week in Review)  
 (bl)  
 By DAVID WALLIS   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
