<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-MAC-REPORT16-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    PalmPilot-Mac software improved
 &HT;    By Charles Haddad
 &HT;    c. 1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   It has been a long time coming but apparently worth the wait. At
least that is the initial review coming from the Internet about
3Com's new Mac software for its PalmPilot line of hand-held
