<HEADLINE>
AMERICA'S MINORITY FARMERS FIGHT `THE LAST PLANTATION': USDA  
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Note potentially offensive word in 18th graf!)   (This excellent 675-word ``separate buy'' article is from the
