   With: FBN-LOPEZ-COLUMN
</P>
<P>
   BKN-BLAZERS (Houston) _ Feature on the Portland Trail Blazers,
who play the Houston Rockets on Tuesday night. By MICHAEL MURPHY.
</P>
<P>
   BKN-ROCKETS (Houston) _ The stumbling Houston Rockets, 13-9,
prepare to take on the 16-4 Portland Trail Blazers. By JONATHAN
FEIGEN.
</P>
</TEXT>
