   &UR; _ Hillary Rodham Clinton &LR;  goes on America Online at 7:45
tonight tues &LR;   &LR; t &LR; o answer questions about ``Dear Socks, Dear Buddy:
Kids' Letters to the First Pets,'' which Amazon.com puts at 9,574th
on its best-seller list.
</P>
<P>
   _ The Bard is so hot that the online service
culturefinder.comcq &LR;  is offering a new 1999 Shakespeare Performance
Finder. The most-performed Shakespeare play in the country right
now _ with 10 productions _ is ``A Midsummer Night's Dream.''
</P>
<P>
   Meanwhile, Education Secretary  &UR; Richard Riley &LR;  announced last
week that the makers of ``Shakespeare in Love'' are producing
``Shakespeare in the Classroom,'' a teaching kit that includes a
video starring  &UR; Gwyneth Paltrow &LR;  and directed by  &UR; John Madden &LR; .
</P>
