   The Seattle Post-Intelligencer plans to move the following for
clients of the NYTimes News Service for editions of Tuesday, March
16, and thereafter. If you have any questions, please call Mary
Downes on the Post-Intelligencer's National/Foreign Desk at (206)
448-8158.
