</P>
<P>
   BBA-MARINERS-TAYLOR (TEMPE, Ariz.) _ Former Yankee No. 1 draft
pick Brien Taylor looks to resume a career he ruined in a fight as
a Yankee minor-leaguer.
</P>
<P>
