and police forces: A sniper shoots and wounds an army officer
driving his jeep down the main road at mid-morning, and the
security forces react swiftly and with full force. A few miles
west, a group of ethnic Albanian villagers stand waiting for a bus
outside the village of Stanovac. As they talk beside the road,
