   ``If someone's willing to cheat on the golf course, they're
probably willing to cheat in a business deal,'' says Titlebaum.
``If they throw clubs and swear, it may tell me they don't have as
much control as I would like for people I want to be associated
with.'' &QL; 
 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; (FIRST OPTIONAL TRIM _ 75 WORDS _ BEGINS HERE AT 750) &LR;  &QC; 
 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Keep an eye out for other clues. Bratti noticed that one
particular client liked to mull things over before making a
